<!-- Definition and uses -->
'''乳果糖'''（{{lang-en|Lactulose}}）是一种不会被吸收的[[糖|糖]]，用来治疗[[便秘|便秘]]和[[高血氨症|高血氨症]]<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=Ham2013>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richard J.|title=Tarascon pocket pharmacopoeia : 2013 classic shirt-pocket edition|date=2013|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|location=Burlington, Ma.|isbn=9781449665869|page=191|edition=27|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=lwueJ4IAl4oC&pg=PA191|access-date=2015-09-02|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511224656/https://books.google.ca/books?id=lwueJ4IAl4oC&pg=PA191|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當治疗便秘時須以口服給藥，治疗肝性脑病时則可以口服或直肠给药<ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|title=Lactulose|url=http://www.drugs.com/monograph/lactulose.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=Aug 11, 2015|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812043555/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/lactulose.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。乳果糖通常在口服8-12小时后起效，但是治疗便秘时則可能需要2天的时间<ref name=Gold2006>{{cite book|last1=Goldman|first1=edited by Ann|last2=Hain|first2=Richard|last3=Liben|first3=Stephen|title=Oxford textbook of palliative care for children|date=2006|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|isbn=9780198526537|page=352|edition=2|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=f1fTsoA4wDMC&pg=PA352|access-date=2015-09-02|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512011141/https://books.google.ca/books?id=f1fTsoA4wDMC&pg=PA352|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Helm2006>{{cite book|last1=Helms|first1=Richard A.|title=Textbook of therapeutics : drug and disease management|date=2006|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Philadelphia, Pa. [u.a.]|isbn=9780781757348|page=1310|edition=8|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=aVmRWrknaWgC&pg=PA1310|access-date=2015-09-02|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512145327/https://books.google.ca/books?id=aVmRWrknaWgC&pg=PA1310|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
乳果糖常见的副作用包含[[腹胀|腹胀]]和腹部绞痛<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。本品也可能导致[[電解質不平衡|电解質平衡問題]]，進而引發[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。目前没有证据表明[[妊娠|妊娠]]期間用藥对胎儿有影响<ref name=AHFS2015/>，哺乳期間用藥也被認為是安全的<ref name=Jones2013>{{cite book|last1=Jones|first1=Wendy|title=Breastfeeding and Medication|date=2013|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9781136178153|page=127|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=0Y8lbCnF1mgC&pg=PA127|access-date=2015-09-02|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513151508/https://books.google.ca/books?id=0Y8lbCnF1mgC&pg=PA127|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本品被分类为渗透通便的药物<ref>{{cite book|last1=Whitlow|first1=Charles|title=Improved Outcomes in Colon and Rectal Surgery.|date=2009|publisher=Informa Healthcare|location=New York|isbn=9781420071535|page=366|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=9FfvBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT378|access-date=2015-09-02|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512032555/https://books.google.ca/books?id=9FfvBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT378|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- History, society and culture -->
乳果糖最早於1929年被首次合成，1950年代後開始用於藥療用途<ref>{{cite book|last1=McSweeney|first1=P.L.H.|last2=Fox|first2=P.F.|title=Advanced dairy chemistry.|date=2009|publisher=Springer-Verlag|location=New York|isbn=9780387848655|page=236|edition=3rd|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=hz9U9nzy-rQC&pg=PA236|access-date=2016-06-18|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513194739/https://books.google.ca/books?id=hz9U9nzy-rQC&pg=PA236|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Schumann|first1=C|title=Medical, nutritional and technological properties of lactulose. An update.|journal=European journal of nutrition|date=November 2002|volume=41 Suppl 1|pages=I17-25|pmid=12420112|doi=10.1007/s00394-002-1103-6}}</ref>。本品列名於[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]，為基礎公衛體系必備藥物之一<ref name=WHO2015E>{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/medicines/publications/essentialmedicines/EML2015_8-May-15.pdf |title=19th WHO Model List of Essential Medicines (April 2015) |date=April 2015 |accessdate=May 10, 2015 |publisher=WHO |archive-date=2015-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150513043105/http://www.who.int/medicines/publications/essentialmedicines/EML2015_8-May-15.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。乳果糖為[[通用名药物|學名藥]]<ref name=Ham2013/>，每劑批發價約 0.18 美金<ref name="Lactulose">{{cite web|title=Lactulose|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=LAC3L&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=3%2E35%20g%2F5%20ml&desc=Lactulose&pack=new&frm=SOLUTION&rte=PO&class_code2=02%2E3%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2802%2E3%2E%29Medicines%20for%20other%20common%20symptoms%20in%20palliative%20care%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=11 August 2015}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，在美國30劑液劑約值20美金<ref name=AHFS2015/>。本品由[[乳糖|乳糖]]製成<ref>{{cite book|last1=Kuntz|first1=Hans-Dieter|title=Hepatology textbook and atlas : history, morphology, biochemistry, diagnostics, clinic, therapy|url=https://archive.org/details/hepatologytextbo00kunt|date=2008|publisher=Springer|location=Heidelberg|isbn=9783540768395|page=[https://archive.org/details/hepatologytextbo00kunt/page/887 887]|edition=3|ref=https://books.google.ca/books?id=oL6d9KuVqLQC&pg=PA887}}</ref>。

